ld use a multipolygon shape","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"atoll: the inner island would be one ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object, while the surrounding","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"group of disconnected but related buildings.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection"}}}